snippet.title: Witch n' Wiz Launch Trailer - A Brand New Game for the NES!
snippet.description:
Witch n' Wiz is a new Puzzle Platformer for the NES, available now!

There are 3 ways to play:

1) FREE in your browser at https://piepacker.com/
2) Download the ROM from https://mhughson.itch.io/witch-n-wiz
3) Buy a LIMITED EDITION Physical Cartridge from https://limitedrungames.com/
